                        <h1>Mercedes-Benz truck oil and Mercedes-Benz van oil</h1>
                        <p xmlns="">Mercedes-Benz trucks, HGVs and light-commercial vehicles can benefit from&nbsp;<br>
high-performance Mobil Delvac&trade; synthetic oils which have been formulated to meet Mercedes-Benz specifications. Whether you need an Actros oil, Atego oil&nbsp;or a Sprinter oil, Mobil Delvac have a comprehensive range you can trust.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <strong>
                                <br>
Mercedes MB-Approval 228.51, 228.31 and 235.28&nbsp;specification oils<br>

                            </strong>
                        </p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <strong><a title="" target="" onclick="trackClick(this);" href="/UK-English-LCW/heavydutyoils_products_engine-oils_mobil-delvac-1-le-5w30.aspx" class=""><img src="../Shared-Images-LCW/product_120x150_mobil-delvac-1-le-5w30-20-litre_eame.jpg" height="100" width="80" alt="Mobil Delvac 1 LE 5W-30" title="Mobil Delvac 1 LE 5W-30" align="left" border="0" hspace="0"></a></strong>
                        </p>

                        <p xmlns="">&nbsp;<a title="" target="" onclick="trackClick(this);" href="/UK-English-LCW/heavydutyoils_products_engine-oils_mobil-delvac-1-le-5w30.aspx" class="">Mobil Delvac 1&trade; LE 5W-30</a> is a low SAPS fully-synthetic diesel engine oil with both Mercedes MB 228.51 approval and Mercedes MB 228.31, and&nbsp;235.28&nbsp;approval, offering both fuel economy potential and long drain capability.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">&nbsp;</p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <strong>Mercedes MB-Approval 228.51 and 235.28</strong><strong>specification oils</strong>
                            <br>

                            <a title="" target="" onclick="trackClick(this);" href="/UK-English-LCW/heavydutyoils_products_engine-oils_mobil-delvac-xhp-esp-10w40.aspx" class="">Mobil Delvac&trade; XHP ESP 10W-40</a> is a low SAPS synthetic oil with Mercedes MB 228.51 and 235.28&nbsp;approval, providing advanced engine and emission system protection.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <strong>Mercedes MB-Approval 228.5 and 235.28&nbsp;specification oils</strong>
                        </p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <strong><a title="" target="" onclick="trackClick(this);" href="/UK-English-LCW/heavydutyoils_products_engine-oils_mobil-delvac-1-5W40.aspx" class=""><img src="../Shared-Images-LCW/product_120x150_mobil-delvac-1-5w40-20-litre_eame.jpg" height="100" width="80" alt="Mobil Delvac 1 5W-40 " title="Mobil Delvac 1 5W-40 " align="left" border="0" hspace="0"></a></strong>
                        </p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <a title="" target="" onclick="trackClick(this);" href="/UK-English-LCW/heavydutyoils_products_engine-oils_mobil-delvac-1-5W40.aspx" class="">Mobil Delvac 1&trade; 5W-40</a> is a fully-synthetic diesel engine oil with Mercedes MB 228.5 and 235.28 approval, delivering exceptional performance and outstanding high and low temperature protection.&nbsp;</p>

                        <p xmlns="">&nbsp;</p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <a title="" target="" onclick="trackClick(this);" href="/UK-English-LCW/heavydutyoils_products_engine-oils_mobil-delvac-xhp-ultra-5w30.aspx" class="">Mobil Delvac&trade; XHP Ultra 5W-30</a> is a synthetic, extra high performance diesel engine oil with Mercedes MB 228.5 and 235.28 approval, providing outstanding protection and fuel economy for modern heavy duty diesel engines used in severe on-highway applications.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <strong>Mercedes MB-Approval 228.5 and 235.27&nbsp;specification oils</strong>
                        </p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <a title="" target="" onclick="trackClick(this);" href="/UK-English-LCW/heavydutyoils_products_engine-oils_mobil-delvac-xhp-extra-10w40.aspx" class="">Mobil Delvac&trade; XHP Extra 10W-40</a> is a synthetic, extra high performance diesel engine oil with Mercedes MB 228.5 and 235.27 approval, and engineered to provide long oil drain intervals in modern diesel engines used in severe on and off-highway applications.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">Use our &lsquo;<a title="" target="" onclick="trackClick(this);" href="/UK-English-LCW/heavydutyoils_mobil-delvac-product-selector.aspx" class="">Which oil</a>&rsquo; tool to find out which oil is right for your Mercedes-Benz commercial vehicle.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <strong>How can you save money by using Mobil Delvac 1&trade;?<br>

                            </strong>Fully synthetic oils such as Mobil Delvac 1 circulate around a Mercedes-Benz engine more easily than traditional mineral oils, so engines operate more efficiently. Mobil Delvac 1 also gets to work faster so your engine reaches peak operating efficiency quicker. Both of these benefits mean your fleet of light or heavy duty vehicles could get more miles per gallon (mpg) and so you save money on diesel.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <strong>How does Mobil Delvac support my Euro IV or Euro V or Euro VI&nbsp;compliant Mercedes-Benz engines?<br>

                            </strong><a title="" target="" onclick="trackClick(this);" href="/UK-English-LCW/heavydutyoils_products_engine-oils_mobil-delvac-1-le-5w30.aspx" class="">Mobil Delvac 1&trade; LE 5W-30</a> and <a title="" target="" onclick="trackClick(this);" href="http://prodwip.mobil.com/UK-English-LCW/heavydutyoils_products_engine-oils_mobil-delvac-xhp-esp-10w40.aspx" class="">Mobil Delvac&trade; XHP ESP 10W-40 </a>with emission system protection contain advanced additives which have been expertly engineered to help prolong the life and maintain the efficiency of emission reduction systems such as the Mercedes-Benz Diesel Particulate Filter (DPF). The DPF is used to fulfil the emission requirements of the Euro IV, Euro V and Euro VI emissions standards.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <strong>How do I find the right oil for my Mercedes-Benz commercial vehicle?<br>

                            </strong>Using the right oil in your truck or light commercial vehicle is important to comply with Mercedes-Benz specifications. Using the right Mobil Delvac product during routine servicing and according to your vehicle&rsquo;s manual will not affect the Mercedes-Benz manufacturer&rsquo;s warranty. You can obtain a recommendation by using the '<a title="" target="" onclick="trackClick(this);" href="/UK-English-LCW/heavydutyoils_mobil-delvac-product-selector.aspx" class="">Which oil</a>' tool and searching by make and model.</p>
